{"tid":2342451,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金希澈的那些美貌女性友人！真的太讓男生們羨慕了～","createTime":"2020-12-27T06:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T11:39:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"daf8090bca238b51112acdd90c0d8f9565a8ee49","tid":2342451,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:45:26.000Z","msg":"作為宇宙大明星，Super Junior的金希澈在娛樂圈也是人脈王，尤其是女性友人還不少，讓不少男生羡慕。<br />\n<br />\n「交際花」金希澈的人脈有多廣呢？ 據說不論性別、年齡和經紀公司，只要和他見過面，他都能迅速和別人親近起來，個人魅力爆棚。 而今天就來說說他的這些人脈中最具代表性的幾位女性友人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n少女時代太妍<br />\n<br />\n金希澈和太妍感情非常好，這是所有粉絲都知道的事情，兩人都是情緒起伏較大的人，因此還被成為「起伏兄妹」。 作為宅女的太妍也公開表示過深交的人不多，金希澈就是其中之一。 金希澈則稱對方是非常喜歡的妹妹，是如果對方不小心落水，他甚至會捨棄生命都要救的人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c3a6248b66a3688a4a117ac281ab250d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-24/132556-890355.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c3a6248b66a3688a4a117ac281ab250d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-24%2F132556-890355.png&h=35bb937d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26adf1de5d3a7e167a824d24b1a088655b43a975","tid":2342451,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"RED VELVET Yeri<br />\n<br />\n作為SM的團寵，RED VELVET的老么Yeri也深得歐巴希澈的喜愛，相差16歲的兩人也經常通過SNS曬合影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4096c1794841f3bee913db25c7a0f9d6/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-24/132556-890356.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4096c1794841f3bee913db25c7a0f9d6%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-24%2F132556-890356.png&h=e0acbe66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全昭彌<br />\n<br />\n金希澈和全昭彌的合影姿勢都很親密，完全就是一對好兄妹，據說金希澈和全昭彌的爸爸私交也很好，相處得就像家人一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3465d60a1cff5921875f14689a490554/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-24/132556-890357.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3465d60a1cff5921875f14689a490554%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-24%2F132556-890357.png&h=240ca23e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b34eabd2c1268180a116495f920632b708b2073","tid":2342451,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:46:15.000Z","msg":"Hani<br />\n<br />\n金希澈的女性友人名單中不能少了Hani，Hani稱歐巴是「長腿叔叔」，是精神支柱一般的存在。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_7d803d0ff160b3b8d535ec26a8234cfa/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-24/132556-890358.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_7d803d0ff160b3b8d535ec26a8234cfa%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-24%2F132556-890358.png&h=3386620b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n孫淡妃<br />\n<br />\n孫淡妃和金希澈也是圈內出了名的至親好友，相差21歲的兩人已經認識了17年，認識這麼就也從未傳出曖昧傳聞，是喝醉酒也能送對方回家且絕對不會傳出緋聞的好姐弟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_591ecb20085835d22b0b8fbcf49e9f5a/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-24/132556-890359.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_591ecb20085835d22b0b8fbcf49e9f5a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-24%2F132556-890359.png&h=34b7ba7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c13740026ff5e25f99502a8eec26a05317ac886","tid":2342451,"uid":339805,"like":30,"dislike":10,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:48:28.000Z","msg":"希澈老師必須死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15b099806d888901ea23cbcbd95955f5867ade6","tid":2342451,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4c13740026ff5e25f99502a8eec26a05317ac886","tid":2342451,"uid":339805,"like":30,"dislike":10,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:48:28.000Z","msg":"希澈老師必須死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86eeab10c6093dfd05e3be45302bf384efe3205","tid":2342451,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"